o Outstanding communication skills, both written and verbal.
o Solid networking and interpersonal skills.
o Able to generate budgets and reports.
o Strong presentation skills, able to explain concepts concisely and accurately.
o Able to develop strong, cooperative relationships with department heads.
o Creative thinking skills and ability to solve problems.

