He/She will work closely with the MEP Team Leader to ensure the continued growth of the MEP Team offering and will be responsible to take technical and commercial ownership of projects assigned.
• Contribute to the growth of Arup’s Plumbing Team ensuring that the Team structure is consistent with workload and the requirements of our Clients (internal and external);
