• Require English skill (spoken & written);
• Knowledge and experience in the design of Data Centre and/or Infrastructure will be an advantage.
• Holding relevant certificates issued by Uptime/ TIA or others recognisable international organizations in the data center industry/ high-tech industry is a significant advantage.

