- Triển khai hoạt động cải tiến hệ thống chất lượng CNTT theo định hướng phát triển chung của công ty và phù hợp tiêu chuẩn ISO 9001, ISO 27001, PCI DSS, ITSM;
- Tham gia đào tạo, hướng dẫn các đơn vị thực hiện đúng quy trình;
- Tham gia ý kiến xây dựng quy chế, chính sách, quy trình, hướng dẫn nghiệp vụ liên quan đến chuyên môn.
- Thực hiện các công việc khác theo phân công.

* Mô tả công việc

New product development
Research market and customer demand to suggest new card product;
Make timeline and deliverables of new product/ plans/ assignments/ tasks;
Coordinate with IT to describe product requirement for system/ tool development/ fixing/ enhancement;
Coordinate with Legal/Process Management to issue regulation and process for credit and debit cards product;
Coordinate with Marketing to develop, launch and manage event/campaign for credit and debit cards product;
Update the Department Head on progress/ status of assigned tasks. Report timely any arising issues ;
Maintain the smoothness of the flow of information between departments/units to get timely updated on operations, avoid duplicated and optimize resources of the division

New card programs development
Research market and customer demand to suggest card acquisition program for credit and debit cards product;
Make timeline and deliverables of new credit and debit card program;
Coordinate with relevant departments/units to launch new credit and debit card programs;

Relationship building
Research, establish and maintain close relationship with big, potential partners to establish/ obtain effective co-brand product exploiting.
Establish and maintain close rapport with all relevant parties such as other departments, divisions, business units, vendors in order to obtain support in delivering desired deliverables

